Hello, I have some info about Minamoto Yoshitsune for
you, he was the half brother to the first Shogun,
Yoritomo Minamoto. Yoshitsune fought for Yoritomo, who
in turn became jealous of Yoshitsune and Yoshitsune
was chased to a small Japanese town, I don't remember
the name of the town, where he later killed himself.
